title: RHUGT Eyebrow Accusations + RHOA Dropping it with Drew

description:
Danny recaps the first 3 episodes of The Real Housewives Ultimate Girls Trip, currently airing on Peacock. After analyzing the chaos of Bluestone Manor, Danny recaps this week's episode of The Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured a Drop it with Drew event and Brooklyn needing a peach and a tagline!


RHOA Recap: 25:06ish
